# AISensy Platform Features Documentation

This document provides a comprehensive breakdown of the features available in the AISensy WhatsApp Business API platform, based on a detailed exploration of the application.

## 1. Dashboard
The central hub for monitoring account health and activity.
- **Key Metrics:**
  - **WhatsApp Business API Status**: Real-time connection status (LIVE/OFFLINE).
  - **Quality Rating**: Meta's quality score for the phone number (High/Medium/Low).
  - **Remaining Quota**: Daily messaging limit (e.g., 1000/24hrs).
  - **WCC Balance**: WhatsApp Conversation Credits for billing.
  - **Payment Status**: Alerts for pending invoices.
- **Quick Actions:**
  - **QR Code**: Link to download the mobile app.
  - **Setup Guide**: Step-by-step checklist for API verification.
  - **Plan Info**: Current subscription details.

## 2. Live Chat (Inbox)
A powerful multi-agent inbox for handling customer conversations.
- **Interface Layout:**
  - **Three-Pane View**: Navigation | Conversation List | Chat Area | Contact Profile.
- **Conversation Management:**
  - **Tabs/Filters**: 
    - **Active**: Ongoing conversations.
    - **Requesting**: New incoming messages waiting for a response.
    - **Intervened**: Conversations taken over by human agents from the bot.
  - **Search**: Find chats by Name or Mobile Number.
- **Message Composition:**
  - **Template Messages**: strict requirement to start conversations outside the 24h window.
  - **Quick Replies**: Pre-set buttons for faster responses.
  - **Media Attachments**: Images, Videos, Documents.
  - **Interactive Messages**: List messages and CTA buttons.
- **Contact Profile (Sidebar):**
  - **Details**: Name, Phone, Status.
  - **Tags**: Add/Remove tags for segmentation (e.g., "Lead", "Customer").
  - **Attributes**: Custom user data fields (e.g., "City", "Order ID").
  - **Notes**: Internal team notes visible only to agents.
  - **Campaign History**: Log of broadcasts sent to the user.

## 3. Contacts (CRM)
A robust contact management system.
- **Management:**
  - **Add Contact**: Manually create single contacts.
  - **Import**: Bulk upload via CSV/Excel (supports up to 200k rows).
  - **Export**: Download contact lists.
- **Segmentation:**
  - **Filtering**: Advanced filters based on Tags, Source, Status, and Attributes.
  - **Smart Lists**: Save filter configurations as dynamic audiences.
- **Data Fields:**
  - **System Fields**: Name, Mobile, Created At.
  - **Custom Attributes**: User-defined fields for personalization.

## 4. Campaigns (Broadcasting)
Tools for sending mass messages to customers.
- **Campaign Types:**
  - **Broadcast**: Standard one-time message blast.
  - **API Campaign**: Triggered via external API calls.
  - **CSV Broadcast**: Send directly from an uploaded file.
  - **Meta Ads**: Create "Click to WhatsApp" advertisements.
- **Creation Flow:**
  1. **Name**: define internal campaign name.
  2. **Audience**: Select from saved segments or upload CSV.
  3. **Message**: Choose a pre-approved Template.
  4. **Variables**: Map template variables (e.g., {{1}} = FirstName).
  5. **Test**: Send a sample to a test number.
  6. **Schedule/Send**: Launch immediately or schedule for later.
- **Analytics:**
  - **Status Tracking**: Sent, Delivered, Read, Failed.
  - **Click Tracking**: CTR for links in messages.

## 5. Flows (Chatbot Builder)
Visual automation tool for creating chatbots.
- **Builder Type:**
  - **Canvas (Drag & Drop)**: Non-linear flow creation.
- **Capabilities:**
  - **Message Nodes**: Text, Image, Video, File.
  - **Interactive Nodes**: Buttons (Reply), Lists.
  - **Logic Nodes**: Conditions, Delays, Random Split.
  - **Actions**: Add Tag, Update Attribute, Notify Admin.
  - **E-commerce**: Show Product Catalog, Multi-Product Messages, Shopify Integration.
  - **Handover**: "Request Intervention" to pass chat to a human agent.

## 6. Management & Settings
Administrative control center.
- **Messaging:**
  - **Templates**: Create, submit, and manage Meta templates (Marketing, Utility, Auth).
  - **Canned Messages**: Create quick snippets for agents.
  - **Opt-in Management**: Rules for handling user consent.
- **Team:**
  - **Users**: Invite team members and assign roles (Admin, Manager, Agent).
  - **Agent Rules**: Auto-assignment based on round-robin or skill.
- **Project:**
  - **API Keys**: Manage API tokens for integration.
  - **Webhooks**: Configure URLs for real-time data push.
  - **Tags & Attributes**: Global management of CRM metadata.
  - **Billing**: Invoices, Credit usage, Subscription plans.
- **General:**
  - **Business Profile**: Profile picture, Description, Address, Website (visible on WhatsApp).

## 7. History & Analytics
- **Message Logs**: Searchable history of every message sent/received system-wide.
- **Detailed Reports**: Agent performance, Message volume, Cost analysis.
